  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722390/extras/ef8db71fa57ac6066951a71cde6186dc.poster.avif?t=1635125619\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722390/extras/ef8db71fa57ac6066951a71cde6186dc.webm?t=1635125619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722390/extras/ef8db71fa57ac6066951a71cde6186dc.mp4?t=1635125619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>History</strong><br><br>Marzia and Sophies mother, Lily, is going through a tough time. She beging drinking too much alcohol, making her violent with her own daughters. Marzia, the eldest, wants to help her by taking to a doctor and enrolling in a group for alcoholics, but she refuses.<br>Now they are in great danger and need to help her as soon as possible.<br><br><strong>Playability</strong><br><br>- <strong>Single Player</strong>.<br>- <strong>Immersive experience</strong>, you don't have to worry about the interface, we want to make it as simple as possible so you can have a fully       immersive experience.<br>- <strong>Collect</strong> the items in order to help your sister escape and help your mother as well.<br>- <strong>Procedural</strong> items on the map.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722390/extras/ef8db71fa57ac6066951a71cde6186dc.poster.avif?t=1635125619\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722390/extras/ef8db71fa57ac6066951a71cde6186dc.webm?t=1635125619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722390/extras/ef8db71fa57ac6066951a71cde6186dc.mp4?t=1635125619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>History</strong><br><br>Marzia and Sophies mother, Lily, is going through a tough time. She beging drinking too much alcohol, making her violent with her own daughters. Marzia, the eldest, wants to help her by taking to a doctor and enrolling in a group for alcoholics, but she refuses.<br>Now they are in great danger and need to help her as soon as possible.<br><br><strong>Playability</strong><br><br>- <strong>Single Player</strong>.<br>- <strong>Immersive experience</strong>, you don't have to worry about the interface, we want to make it as simple as possible so you can have a fully       immersive experience.<br>- <strong>Collect</strong> the items in order to help your sister escape and help your mother as well.<br>- <strong>Procedural</strong> items on the map.",
